{"title":"SQL Quick Reference","html":"<h1 id=\"sql-quick-reference\">SQL Quick Reference</h1>\n<p>Quick SQL reference guide.</p>\n<h2 id=\"basic-queries\">Basic Queries</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">SELECT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> * </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> table</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">SELECT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> col1, col2 </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> table</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> WHERE</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> condition;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">INSERT INTO</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> table</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> VALUES</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> (val1, val2);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">UPDATE</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> table</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> SET</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> col = val </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">WHERE</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> condition;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">DELETE</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> FROM</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> table</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> WHERE</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> condition;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"joins\">Joins</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A9955\">-- INNER JOIN</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">SELECT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> * </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> t1 </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">JOIN</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> t2 </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">ON</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> t1.id = t2.id;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A9955\">-- LEFT JOIN</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">SELECT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> * </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> t1 </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">LEFT JOIN</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> t2 </span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">ON</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> t1.id = t2.id;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"aggregations\">Aggregations</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">SELECT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> col, </span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\">COUNT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(*), </span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\">AVG</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(num) </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#569CD6\"> table</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">GROUP BY</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> col </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#569CD6\">HAVING</span><span style=\"color:#DCDCAA\"> COUNT</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">(*) > </span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">5</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Remember</strong>: Practice SQL regularly!</p>\n","source":"19-sql-database-fundamentals/sql-database-quick-reference.md","githubUrl":"https://github.com/NabidAlam/road-to-machine-learning/blob/main/19-sql-database-fundamentals/sql-database-quick-reference.md","module":"19-sql-database-fundamentals","lessonId":"sql-database-quick-reference","guideId":null,"type":"module"}